  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] they're calling it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Everything is automats.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the protectors-- then I, I told the, the commander.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He is a major.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I tell him I need 28 people or 50 people or 40 people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It's different how far we doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We doing small, I need less people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they are behind us to cover us if something happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we, we did organize very good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Yeah, I was one of the top professionals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And when it was meetings from our group in the [NON-ENGLISH] division or [NON-ENGLISH] army, I was speaking.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I was the top man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I-- yeah, all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "98%, oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I, I run this place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I didn't tell him to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I tell him to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I run the place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was with them [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Frightened, frightened, I, I, I was never frightened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why should I be frightened?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was never frightened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We have got-- we have got grenades with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got four all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Something happen, I blow myself up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's over.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's no use to, to, to be and do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I talk to him immediately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, when I took him out, I talked to him immediately.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told him right away, I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, all the questions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We ask them, normally-- first of all, we start from what city he is, his name, his birth, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After that, what his family doing, same thing as you ask.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And done it slowly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we don't move in right away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they knew, if, if they don't take-- if they don't tell me the truth, I know more or less what division is in the front.",
